name: ten minutes before war
description:
Year 2075.
40 years how we almost destroyed Earth in Great gas war.
10 years how we colonized Mars.
9 years how 95% of humanity died to unknown virus.
5 years how we met alien life form.
1 year how we colonized Saturn.
6 months how we have a tense relationship with the Saturnanians.
One day since the first blood was shed.
